{"id": "ChIJI851cQDbwoARt-R-30Lhyi8", "rating": 4.8, "userRatingCount": 17, "displayName": {"text": "Unreal Poke", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJI851cQDbwoARt-R-30Lhyi8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tocVVWcElWRUZrVFZvM1RGcDJMVVZaUWtRMmEwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Arcadia finally got a solid new spot! Unreal Poke just took over the old boba place on Baldwin, and it is already a massive hit with the locals. I walked in and the place was absolutely packed with a long line, but honestly, once you step inside, you can see why. It smells incredible and tastes even better.\n\nI tried the Inari Poke stuffed with tuna, and it was so good and perfectly seasoned, fresh, and just bursting with flavor. Even with the huge opening crowd, the staff handles the rush like pros. The service was super efficient, so the line moves fast. Plus, the whole interior has this awesome, vibrant Hawaiian style that makes the vibe really fun.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Arcadia finally got a solid new spot! Unreal Poke just took over the old boba place on Baldwin, and it is already a massive hit with the locals. I walked in and the place was absolutely packed with a long line, but honestly, once you step inside, you can see why. It smells incredible and tastes even better.\n\nI tried the Inari Poke stuffed with tuna, and it was so good and perfectly seasoned, fresh, and just bursting with flavor. Even with the huge opening crowd, the staff handles the rush like pros. The service was super efficient, so the line moves fast. Plus, the whole interior has this awesome, vibrant Hawaiian style that makes the vibe really fun.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "regis kwong", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111212127579957762328/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUl8HquiHw9l5QMQ5U7ZfHcwVlgDIGHJeKbXiJ8K0pzF75VSytlaA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba8"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-21T03:58:01.480981673Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tocVVWcElWRUZrVFZvM1RGcDJMVVZaUWtRMmEwRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tocVVWcElWRUZrVFZvM1RGcDJMVVZaUWtRMmEwRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2db007175ce23:0x2fcae142df7ee4b7"}, {"name": "places/ChIJI851cQDbwoARt-R-30Lhyi8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2toeVRUbHRZek5ZWkZBNFgzTmFjbEpsVEhWUFNGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Food was amazing.  Visited durring thier grand opening celebration.  Great vibes and and even better food.  Not your typical poke spot and that is a good thing.  If you are craving an authentic style of poke that is made with great care this is the place.  The sides are great.  The fact that they have fresh fish flown in from Hawaii for thier premium poke shows how much they care.\n\nGive this place a try and add this your rotation...you will be happy you did.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Food was amazing.  Visited durring thier grand opening celebration.  Great vibes and and even better food.  Not your typical poke spot and that is a good thing.  If you are craving an authentic style of poke that is made with great care this is the place.  The sides are great.  The fact that they have fresh fish flown in from Hawaii for thier premium poke shows how much they care.\n\nGive this place a try and add this your rotation...you will be happy you did.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Albert Maldonado", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110490959270202636962/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX1A6ExUjXEq8sg832JUdEnch2EVlBdM5hn2Se2FfhqpyH3NCeW=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-21T00:22:30.029201741Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.co